text: Kitson Kapiriel (born December 10, 1993) is a sprinter from the Federated States of Micronesia. He competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in the men's 100 metres race; his time of 11.42 seconds in the preliminary round did not qualify him for the first round. ==References== Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Federated States of Micronesia male sprinters Category:Olympic track and field athletes of the Federated States of Micronesia Category:Athletes (track and field) at the 2016 Summer Olympics
